\b0\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 Then Job answered and said:\uc0\u8232 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 2
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 "Oh, that my grief were fully weighed, And my calamity laid with it on the scales! 
\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl180\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 3
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 For then it would be heavier than the sand of the sea-- Therefore my words have been rash. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 4
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 For the arrows of the Almighty are within me; My spirit drinks in their poison; The terrors of God are arrayed against me. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 5
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Does the wild donkey bray when it has grass, Or does the ox low over its fodder? 
